               <p>I am a <rs id="t17770409-69-viclabel336" type="occupation">cheesemonger</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17770409-69-victim587 t17770409-69-viclabel336"></join>: I saw the prisoner take 8 lb. of bacon off my stall and go away with it; I sent my servant after him, who brought him back with the bacon upon him.</p>
